f\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58b6b38bd098833280dcbb448c9faa7cf69a2bfe","tid":2510563,"uid":39710,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T09:04:39.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">香港差佬！<br />\n屌你老母！</span>"},{"pid":"fc5e83fd2256b60bfb390ba0c0060b230a3a0849","tid":2510563,"uid":74361,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T09:04:45.000Z","msg":"廁所爆粗 傅穎打冷震<br />\n2008年4月29日<br />\n<br />\n  鄭融 昨日出席「小記者童心看奧運啟動禮」活動，接受小學生訪問，她笑言印象中的記者形象往往就是戰地記者或是政治記者，工作太危險，她笑說：「當記者的一係做人質，一係做犯人。圈中只有何韻詩 有鮮明的政治立場，她有膽在網頁內指CNN記者不尊重華人是種族歧視，我很佩服她。」<br />\n<br />\n  同場的傅穎 （Theresa）就談及日前在森美 的棟篤笑中被指講粗口，她解釋說：「因為有報章將我所講那句改為『黐X線』，大家才以為我講粗口。」她又笑稱在中學時試過在廁所內對自己講了一句「X街」，之後自己卻嚇得整個人打冷震，從此便不敢再試。"},{"pid":"94e177c0f632b2ff1fc1f6fb1c5b48cb2e794fed","tid":2510563,"uid":166405,"like":5,"dislike":10,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T09:05:22.000Z","msg":"潘景臨在制服李小龍前曾大叫「屌你老母！襲警！」<br />\n估唔到李小龍咁廢連黑警都打唔贏<br />\n之前班國術撚仲吹到話打贏泰臣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb50031c3399016576b523573b65edf9d0c32935","tid":2510563,"uid":149662,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"quote":{"pid":"8c32af181488e01333c1f67ebc5a830c80b3de3f","tid":2510563,"uid":78039,"like":127,"dislike":6,"score":121,"citedBy":11,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T08:58:07.000Z","msg":"警員識聽Don't insult my intelligence<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有d料到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T09:06:44.000Z","msg":"法庭有翻譯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5b73332c32978abdc9bc99df50366b1068ce3dc","tid":2510563,"uid":322130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T09:06:49.000Z","msg":"logic廢到卜街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e30142d09c9f31afafb21cccb4253bdb369fb89","tid":2510563,"uid":24296,"like"